---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms and Conditions — xCrypto24" description="Terms of service for xCrypto24. Understand usage rights, data accuracy disclaimers, and limitation of liability for our free crypto tracker." keywords="xcrypto24 terms, crypto tracker terms of service, limitation of liability, acceptable use">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebPage","name":"Terms and Conditions — xCrypto24","url":"https://xcrypto24.com/terms","description":"Terms of service for xCrypto24. Understand usage rights, data accuracy disclaimers, and limitation of liability for our free crypto tracker."})} />
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:2rem auto;padding:0 1rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Terms and Conditions</h1>
    <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">Last updated: June 2026 · Effective immediately</p>

    <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2rem;">By accessing xCrypto24.com ("the Service"), you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, do not use the Service. These terms apply to all users, visitors, and anyone who accesses the Service.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">1. Nature of the Service</h2>
    <div style="margin:1rem 0;padding:1.2rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.1);">
      <p style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:#f87171;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">⚠️ Critical Disclaimer</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;">xCrypto24 is an <strong>information-only tool</strong>. We are NOT a financial advisor, broker, exchange, wallet, custodian, or investment platform. We do not hold, transfer, or manage cryptocurrency. We do not provide financial advice.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">2. No Financial Advice</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">Nothing on this website constitutes financial, investment, trading, or tax advice. All data displayed (prices, market caps, safety scores, trends) is for informational purposes only. You are solely responsible for your own investment decisions. Always consult a qualified financial advisor before making investment decisions.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">3. Data Accuracy</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">All data is sourced from third-party APIs (DexScreener, RugCheck, GeckoTerminal). We provide this data "as is" without warranty. Data may be delayed, inaccurate, or incomplete. We are not responsible for errors in third-party data feeds.</p>
    <div style="margin:1rem 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0.75rem;">
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.08);"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#fca5a5;">Prices may be delayed or differ from live exchange rates</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.08);"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#fca5a5;">Safety scores are algorithmic assessments, not guarantees</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.08);"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#fca5a5;">Market cap and volume data depends on third-party reporting</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.08);"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#fca5a5;">Token listings do not constitute endorsement or recommendation</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">To the maximum extent permitted by law, xCrypto24, its operators, developers, and affiliates shall NOT be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from:</p>
    <div style="margin:1rem 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0.75rem;">
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Financial losses from trading decisions made using our data</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Inaccurate, delayed, or missing data from third-party sources</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Service interruptions, downtime, or data loss</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Losses from tokens that are rugged, scammed, or devalued</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Any actions taken based on safety scores or trend indicators</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">5. Acceptable Use</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">You agree NOT to:</p>
    <div style="margin:1rem 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0.75rem;">
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.08);"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#fca5a5;">Use automated scraping or bots to extract data at scale</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.08);"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#fca5a5;">Attempt to exploit, hack, or disrupt the service</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.08);"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#fca5a5;">Use the service to promote scams, fraud, or manipulation</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.08);"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#fca5a5;">Impersonate our service or claim affiliation</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">The xCrypto24 name, logo, design, code, and original content are the property of xCrypto24. Third-party data (prices, logos, token information) belongs to their respective owners.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">7. Service Availability</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">We provide the service free of charge with no uptime guarantee. We may modify, suspend, or discontinue any feature at any time without notice. We reserve the right to restrict access for any reason.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">8. Governing Law</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of England and Wales. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms. Check this page periodically.</p>

    <div style="margin-top:2rem;text-align:center;">
      <a href="/" style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.85rem;text-decoration:none;">← Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
